    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus with one living species of rare squirrel-like primate and one recently extinct, perhaps within the past 500 years, from Madagascar. They date to the Holocene.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
